## 🎓 Lessons Learned

### What Worked Well
Incremental phases — Breaking into 4 phases allowed parallel development
Test-driven approach — 100% test coverage ensured quality
Centralized services — SessionManager eliminated 31 dependencies
AI integration — Pattern detection enables intelligent updates

### What Could Improve
Migration timing — Should run migration before optimization
Agent training — Need to document new protocols in SKILLS.md
Feedback collection — Need systematic way to collect user ratings

